<ab><lb n="1"/>  <gap reason="lost" unit="character" quantity="3"/>  <lb n="2"/><gap reason="lost" unit="character" quantity="10"/> <orig n="unresolved">σ</orig><gap reason="lost" unit="character" quantity="2"/>  <lb n="3"/><gap reason="lost" unit="character" quantity="5"/><w lemma="ὁ"><supplied reason="lost">τὸ</supplied><unclear reason="damage">ν</unclear></w> <w lemma="παῖς">παῖδα</w> <lb n="4"/><supplied reason="lost"><w lemma="αὐτός">αὐτοῦ</w></supplied> <w lemma="διά">διὰ</w>  <w lemma="ψήφισμα">ψηφίσ<lb n="5" break="no"/><supplied reason="lost">ματ</supplied>ος</w> <w lemma="καί">καὶ</w> <w lemma="μεταλλάζω">μετηλ<lb n="6" break="no"/><supplied reason="lost">λά</supplied>κοτα</w>  <w lemma="τιμάω">τειμηθῆ<lb n="7" break="no"/><supplied reason="lost">ναι δὲ</supplied></w> <w lemma="καί">καὶ</w> <w lemma="αὐτός">αὐτὸν</w> <g ref="#star"/>  <lb n="8"/><w lemma="ὑπό"><supplied reason="lost">ὑπὸ</supplied></w>  <w lemma="ὁ"><supplied reason="lost">τ</supplied>ῆς</w> <w lemma="βουλή">βουλῆς</w> <lb n="9"/>καὶ τοῦ<w lemma="δῆμος"><unclear reason="damage">δήμ</unclear><supplied reason="lost">ου</supplied></w> <gap reason="lost" unit="character" quantity="4"/>  <lb n="10"/><gap reason="lost" unit="character" quantity="3"/>  </ab>
</div>
         <div type="apparatus">
            <p>Something like  . . .<supplied reason="lost">τειμῆ</supplied>σ<supplied reason="lost">αι δὲ καὶ τὸ</supplied>ν παῖδα <supplied reason="lost">αὐτοῦ</supplied> may have stood in ll. 1-3</p>
         </div>
         <div type="translation">
            <p> . . . ] that his] son [be honoured] in a decree also after his death and for him too to be praised by the Council and the People [ . . .</p>
         </div>
         <div type="commentary">
            <p>This is perhaps part of a decision of the Council that a father as well as his deceased son should be honoured; it probably concluded by urging the father to bear his loss with courage. For the combination of elements cf. <ref type="inscription" n="1507" target="120704.xml"/>a (=MAMA 512)</p>
         </div>
